	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ne diutius mireris, amicorum incomparabilis, cur scribendi ad te officium tam diu intermiserim, scito me iam pridem statuisse in dies iter ad vos arripere meque vivam fore epistolam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum, cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispani</placeName> milites ante duos fere menses <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l245" cert="high">Kauffbuͤrnam</placeName> ingressi essent, miseram alioqui plebeculam molestaturi, non licuit mihi domum meam deserere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cumque ipsis tritis istic 6 septimanis tandem hinc solvissent nihilque periculi amplius ex illis imminere videbatur, ego <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l907" cert="high">Campidunum</placeName> usque <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetios</placeName> visitaturus veneram, ecce per feredarium certior fio Hispanos ex improviso <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l245" cert="high">Kauffburnam</placeName> rediisse sturmatimque, ut dicitur, primo impetu in aedes meas irruisse, uxorem, liberos et generum meum ex diversoriis suis sub tegulas quasi cedere coegisse, me quesiisse et minas feroces sparsisse propter nescio quas calumnias, quibus ingratum et cęcum vulgus, ut audio, mihi imposuit, ita ut ne domi quidem meę tutus sim neque consultum sit longius a familia proficisci, donec audiam, quo tragedię huius finis tendat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Delitescendum igitur mihi destinavi hinc inde et consyderandum, remne fuga an alio quopiam consilio agam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnino autem deo duce hac estate <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerum</persName> meum invisam; ipse dominum pro me orat, ne supra vires me tentari sinat.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Erectus porro dei benignitate atque constans in pietatis proposito sum, utut mundus insaniat.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu tecum inito rationem, quomodo <persName ref="p8354" cert="high">Lętus</persName> cum suis reliquum huius vitę curriculum instituat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgenses</placeName> adhuc inconcussi violencię obsistunt dantque argumenta diuturnę perseverancię; ego vero illis propter non satis puram religionem timeo, spero tamen dominum ipsis, si conscientiis bonis ita ambulant, miserturum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Princeps <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniarum</placeName> hinc properat abiissetque iam, nisi pyratę, ut fama est, iter insecurum fęcissent.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Cęsare</persName> scribere ne verbum quidem licet.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominos <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p21096" cert="high">Blaureros</persName> fratres, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4082" cert="high">Zviccium</persName>, simmistas tuos, dominos consules, item <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4637" cert="high">Diterichum</persName> in Ror universosque bonos, presertim exquestorem illum exulem, salvos esse cupio; vide, ne <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName> meum pretereas.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l907" cert="high">Campiduni</placeName> 14. maii 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8354" cert="high">G[eorgius] L[aetus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henricho Bullingero</persName>, antistiti ecclesię <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName>, domino et amico incomparabili suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
